\c 36
\s Jehoahazi, naJehoyakimu,
\s naJehoyakini madzimambo aJudha
\p
\v 1 Ipapo vanhu venyika iyo vakatora Jehoahazi mwanakomana waJosia, vakamuita mambo panzvimbo yababa vake paJerusaremu.
\p
\v 2 Joahazi akatanga kubata ushe ava namakore makumi maviri namatatu, akabata ushe paJerusaremu mwedzi mitatu.
\v 3 Mambo weIjipiti akamubvisa paushe paJerusaremu, akaripisa nyika matarenta esirivha ane zana, netarenta rimwe rendarama.
\v 4 Mambo weIjipiti akagadza Eriyakimi munun'una wake ave mambo waJudha neJerusaremu, akashandura zita rake, rikazova Jehoyakimu. Neko akatora munun'una wake Joahazi, akaenda naye Ijipiti.
\p
\v 5 Jehoyakimu akatanga kubata ushe ava namakore makumi maviri namashanu; akabata ushe paJerusaremu makore gumi nerimwe, akaita zvakaipa pamberi paJehovha Mwari wake.
\v 6 Zvino Nebhukadhinezari mambo weBhabhironi akasvika kuzorwa naye, akamusunga naketani, kundomuisa Bhabhironi.
\v 7 Nebhukadhinezari akaendawo nedzimwe nhumbi dzeimba yaJehovha akadziisa Bhabhironi.
\v 8 Zvino mamwe mabasa aJehoyakimu, nezvinonyangadza zvake zvaakaita, nezvakawanikwa maari, tarirai zvakanyorwa mubhuku yamadzimambo aIsiraeri naJudha; Jehoyakini mwanakomana wake akamutevera paushe.
\p
\v 9 Jehoyakini akatanga kubata ushe ava namakore masere, akabata ushe paJerusaremu mwedzi mitatu namazuva ane gumi; akaita zvakaipa pamberi paJehovha.
\v 10 Zvino gore rikati rapera mambo Nebhukadhinezari akatuma nhume vakamuisa Bhabhironi, pamwechete nenhumbi dzinokosha dzeimba yaJehovha, akaita munun'una wake Zedhekia mambo waJudha neJerusaremu.
\s Zedhekia mambo
\s wokupedzisira waJudha
\p
\v 11 Zedhekia akatanga kubata ushe ava namakore makumi maviri nerimwe; akabata ushe paJerusaremu makore gumi nerimwe.
\v 12 Akaita zvakaipa pamberi paJehovha Mwari wake; haana kuzvininipisa pamberi pomuporofita Jeremiya, aitaura mashoko aibva pamurumo waJehovha.
\s Nebhukadhinezari anoputsa
\s Jerusaremu nokutapa vaJudha
\p
\v 13 Akamukirawo mambo Nebhukadhinezari, akanga amupikisa naMwari; asi akawomesa mutsipa wake, nokuomesa mwoyo wake, akarega kutendeukira kuna Jehovha Mwari waIsiraeri.
\v 14 Uye vakuru vose vapirisiti navanhu vakadarika zvikuru kwazvo, vakatevera zvinonyangadza zvose zvavahedheni, vakasvibisa imba yaJehovha yaakanga atsaura paJerusaremu.
\v 15 Jehovha Mwari wamadzibaba avo akatuma mashoko kwavari nenhume dzake, achifumira mangwanani achituma; nokuti akanga ane tsitsi navanhu vake uye nenzvimbo yake;
\v 16 asi vakaseka nhume dzaMwari, vakazvidza mashoko ake, vakadadira vaporofita vake, kusvikira Jehovha atsamwira vanhu vake, kusvikira vasichagoni kurapwa.
\p
\v 17 Saka wakauyisa mambo wavaKaradhea kwavari akauraya majaya avo nomunondo paimba yavo tsvene; haana kunzwira tsitsi kunyange jaya, kana musikana, kana mutana, kana akachena vhudzi; akavaisa vose muruoko rwake.
\v 18 Nhumbi dzosewo dzeimba yaMwari, huru neduku, nepfuma yeimba yaJehovha, nepfuma yamambo neyamachinda ake, akazviisa zvose Bhabhironi.
\v 19 Vakapisa imba yaMwari, vakaputsa rusvingo rweJerusaremu, vakapisa dzimba dzose dzoushe dzaro nomoto, vakaparadza nhumbi dzose dzinokosha dzaro.
\v 20 Avo vakanga vapukunyuka pamunondo, akaenda navo Bhabhironi; vakandova varanda vake navanakomana vake kusvikira ushe uchibatwa navaPeresia;
\v 21 kuti shoko raJehovha, rakanga rarehwa nomuromo waJeremiya, riitike; kusvikira nyika yafarira maSabata ayo, nokuti panguva yose yokuparadzwa kwayo yakachengeta maSabata, ikasvitsa makore ana makumi manomwe.
\s Korestti mamto weVerisia notendera vaJudha kudzoka
\p
\v 22 Zvino negore rokutanga raKoreshi mambo wePerisia, kuti shoko raJehovha rakanga rarehwa nomuromo waJeremiya riitike, Jehovha akamutsa mweya waKoreshi mambo wePerisia, akaparidza paushe hwake hwose, akazvinyorawo, achiti,
\v 23 "Zvanzi naKoreshi mambo wePerisia, `Jehovha Mwari wokudenga akandipa ushe hwose hwenyika, akandiraira kuti ndimuvakire imba paJerusaremu riri paJudha. " `Ani naani aripo pakati penyu wavanhu vake, Jehovha Mwari wake ngaave naye, ngaakwire hake ko.' "
